E. Soft Clauses (Persona-Extended)
\f0\b0\fs53\fsmilli26667 \cf8 \

\f1\b\fs24 \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \
\
{{\NeXTGraphic Pasted Graphic 16.png \width25120 \height17360 \appleattachmentpadding0 \appleembedtype0 \appleaqc
}洞\
