\f15\b0 \cf0 \uc0\u916 
\f5 \uc0\u8346 
\f15  is the maximum number of times a honeypot's persona can change in a given zone across the entire planning horizon H. It bounds how frequently the operations team must create new fake identities, update AD accounts, rotate certificates, and reconfigure traffic patterns.\
