\f13 \uc0\u7496 
\f15  never drops below \uc0\u964 
\f13 \uc0\u7496 
\f20 \uc0\u8304 
\f15  \'d7 (1 \uc0\u8722  1.0/0.8). This prevents the formula from producing degenerate results even when threat intelligence reports unrealistically high probabilities.\
